content: How much do I owe in taxes?

Tax rate,Taxable income threshold
3.35%, on the portion of taxable income that is $79950 or less, plus
6.60%, on the portion of taxable income over $79950 up to $193300 plus
7.60%, on the portion of taxable income over $193300 up to $294600 plus
8.75%, on the portion of taxable income over $294600
